			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Amaute’ zomah Hakkoz’ tapa Uriah, a tapa Meremoth in ama khawk sung puah hi. Tua zomah Meshezabel’ tapa Berekhiah, a tapa Meshullam hi a, tua zomah Baana’ tapa Zadok in puah hi.",
