			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mizpah gam a uk, Kolhozeh’ tapa Shallum in Tuinak Kongpi puah a, tua kongpi bawlpha-in a kongkhakte a kalhna bulh hi. Tua ciangin amah in kumpipa’ huan gei-a kulh ciang a, David khuapi pana hong paisuk kahlei ciang dong a sem hi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ama zomah Bethzur gam phelkhat a uk, Azbuk’ tapa Nehemiah in David’ han san ciang, a kibawl tawm bual le Galkap Inn ciang dong puah hi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ama zomah a puah Levi mite: Bani’ tapa Rehum hi a, ama zomah Keilah gam phelkhat a uk Hashabiah in ama gam tangin puah hi.",
